        <updateDate>2021-01-28T19:49:24Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>National Collegiate Athletics Act of 2019 or the NCAA Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill establishes protections for student-athletes. For example, the bill establishes minimum duration requirements for certain sports scholarships and requires institutions of higher education to provide medical coverage with respect to student-athlete injuries.</p> <p>The bill also modifies provisions related to collective bargaining agreements in professional sports and work opportunities for student-athletes.</p>  ]]></text>
      </summary>
